---
// src/pages/index.astro
---

<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
    <title>Feliz Dia dos Namorados</title>
    
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;800&display=swap');

      :root {
        --rosa-pastel: #ffe6ea;
        --vermelho-texto: #800020;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; 
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background-color: var(--rosa-pastel);
        background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width='60' height='60' viewBox='0 0 60 60' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M30 20c-3-6-10-6-14-1-4 5-3 12 0 16l14 14 14-14c3-4 4-11 0-16-4-5-11-5-14 1z' fill='%23ffb3c1' fill-opacity='0.6' fill-rule='evenodd'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
        color: var(--vermelho-texto);
        min-height: 100dvh; 
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        overflow-x: hidden; 
        padding: 5vw; 
      }

      .conteudo-principal {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 400px; 
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .cartao-vidro {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: 24px 20px 32px 20px;
        text-align: center;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(255, 179, 193, 0.5);
      }

      /* NOVO: Estilo para o Cartão de Imagem */
      .cartao-foto {
        width: 100%;
        height: 240px; /* Altura ideal para mobile */
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        border: 4px solid white; /* Moldura estilo foto antiga/polaroid */
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      }

      .cartao-foto img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover; /* Faz a foto preencher o espaço sem distorcer */
        display: block;
      }

      .icone-coracao {
        width: 44px;
        height: 44px;
        fill: #ff4d6d;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        animation: pulsar 2s infinite;
      }

      @keyframes pulsar {
        0% { transform: scale(1); }
        50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        100% { transform: scale(1); }
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 8vw, 2.2rem);
        font-weight: 800;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        color: #590d22;
      }

      .texto-principal {
        font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 4vw, 1.05rem);
        color: #800f2f;
        line-height: 1.5;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .botao {
        display: inline-block;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 16px 20px;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        color: white;
        background-color: #ff4d6d;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 77, 109, 0.3);
      }

      .botao:active {
        transform: scale(0.96);
        background-color: #c9184a;
      }

      .mini-cartoes {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .mini-cartao {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .mini-cartao h2 {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #590d22;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .mini-cartao p {
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        color: #800f2f;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <div class="conteudo-principal">
      <div class="cartao-vidro">
        
        <div class="cartao-foto">
          <img 
            src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516589178581-6cd7833ae3b2?q=80&w=600&auto=format&fit=crop" 
            alt="Nossa Foto Especial" 
          />
        </div>

        <svg class="icone-coracao" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"/>
        </svg>
        
        <h1>Feliz Dia dos<br/>Namorados</h1>
        
        <p class="texto-principal">
          Cada momento ao seu lado é uma nova razão para celebrar o nosso amor. Obrigado por fazer todos os dias serem especiais.
        </p>
        
      </div>

      <div class="mini-cartoes">
        <div class="mini-cartao">
          <h2>Momentos</h2>
          <p>Adicione aqui pequenos momentos e memórias.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </body>
</html>
